enture 02: The Beginning","video":false,"overview":"In 2012, after the events of Digimon Adventure: Last Evolution Kizuna, the early adulthood DigiDestined—Daisuke, Miyako, Iori, Takeru Takashi, Hikari, and Ken—must reconcile their new responsibilities with their Digimon partners. But Rui Owada, a mysterious young man,  appears, claiming to be the first human to partner with a Digimon–Ukkomon. Could Rui really have been the first-ever DigiDestined?","genre_ids":[16,12,14],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.8727,"vote_count":41,"poster_path":"/adRK2KTle05DTKcrkaAMAJzrLzh.jpg","release_date":"2023-04-01","vote_average":7.037,"backdrop_path":"/stgwLe5ixbMzirxWpnxhJyGBHUg.jpg","original_title":"デジモンアドベンチャー02 THE BEGINNING","original_language":"ja"},{"id":900783,"adult":false,"title":"The Kashmir Files","video":false,"overview":"Based on a true tragedy, the emotionally triggering film sheds light on the plight of Kashmiri Pandits (Hindus), a religious minority in the 1990s Kashmir valley, who were compelled to flee their homes by the Islamic militants.","genre_ids":[36,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.5862,"vote_count":85,"poster_path":"/2VvjJFDBFYkVgr89BjqbUl26QyW.jpg","release_date":"2022-03-11","vote_average":7.012,"backdrop_path":"/o0lQnIaYo5N05mfsltdl3ZCAXpa.jpg","original_title":"द कश्मीर फ़ाइल्स","original_language":"hi"},{"id":267970,"adult":false,"title":"Miss Hokusai","video":false,"overview":"A daughter is constantly overshadowed by her famous father, but she is determined to make her own mark in the world.","genre_ids":[16,18,36],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.6641,"vote_count":153,"poster_path":"/21botnUdVFVeg2nb8j5SHfupWD9.jpg","release_date":"2015-05-09","vote_average":6.68,"backdrop_path":"/kWT9hKpbd0MhvQ38Dga1KAVMrqU.jpg","original_title":"百日紅 〜Miss HOKUSAI〜","original_language":"ja"},{"id":27130,"adult":false,"title":"I Walked with a Zombie","video":false,"overview":"A nurse in the Caribbean turns to voodoo in hopes of curing her patient, a mindless woman whose husband she's fallen in love with.","genre_ids":[9648,27,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.7178,"vote_count":321,"poster_path":"/uoyBR8XNxPQRojujtczfG1qJezY.jpg","release_date":"1943-04-21","vote_average":6.791,"backdrop_path":"/bCyK6eETwA6kzxLxDDuwJ3l7Wdw.jpg","original_title":"I Walked with a Zombie","original_language":"en"}],"similar_content":[{"id":1058619,"adult":false,"title":"Divinity","video":false,"overview":"Two brothers crash into the decaying Earth to stop a capitalist from manufacturing an immortality serum, which is synthesized utilizing heinous methods and leaving an increasingly dire infertility rate in its wake.","genre_ids":[878,14,27],"popularity":2.2141,"vote_count":43,"poster_path":"/3Ri4XxXNCUKwlZWXgoVNftF7GIY.jpg","release_date":"2023-10-13","vote_average":5.2,"backdrop_path":"/iu5RMfBVlU4v0drskl7sx3Gai0s.jpg","original_title":"Divinity","original_language":"en"},{"id":3422,"adult":false,"title":"Lady Caliph","video":false,"overview":"La Califfa's husband was killed during the strikes so she takes the side of the strikers. Her conflict with the plant owner Doverdo gradually  turns into a love relationship.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.4779,"vote_count":23,"poster_path":"/9gSM7ZGBLW5RuuQucRyVJNHCztc.jpg","release_date":"1970-12-31","vote_average":5.3,"backdrop_path":"/zK8UKm0FprxvaX2HO9NH5tyHjrM.jpg","original_title":"La Califfa","original_language":"it"},{"id":2992,"adult":false,"title":"Appetite","video":false,"overview":"The guests of the Station Hotel have assembled to play a game of cards. The loser will sleep in room 207, a room rumored to be haunted. It hasn't been slept in for 20 years.  As their lives tangle in a paranoid deadlock, the only escape becomes murder.","genre_ids":[27,53],"popularity":0.2386,"vote_count":7,"poster_path":"/jkXx2LHwpbmLyurhzA3AsMs1Pth.jpg","release_date":"1998-08-12","vote_average":2.786,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Appetite","original_language":"en"},{"id":3082,"adult":false,"title":"Modern Times","video":false,"overview":"A bumbling tramp desires to build a home with a young woman, yet is thwarted time and time again by his lack of experience and habit of being in the wrong place at the wrong time..","genre_ids":[35,18,10749],"popularity":4.2486,"vote_count":4004,"poster_path":"/7uoiKOEjxBBW0AgDGQWrlfGQ90w.jpg","release_date":"1936-02-05","vote_average":8.282,"backdrop_path":"/kSlO1pHpwQfPQdgVPr7dJiJNtJ8.jpg","original_title":"Modern Times","original_language":"en"},{"id":614,"adult":false,"title":"Wild Strawberries","video":false,"overview":"Crotchety retired doctor Isak Borg travels from Stockholm to Lund, Sweden, with his pregnant and unhappy daughter-in-law, Marianne, in order to receive an honorary degree from his alma mater. Along the way, they encounter a series of hitchhikers, each of whom causes the elderly doctor to muse upon the pleasures and failures of his own life. These include the vivacious young Sara, a dead ringer for the doctor's own first love.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":1.7167,"vote_count":1773,"poster_path":"/iyTD2QnySNMPUPE3IedZQipSWfz.jpg","release_date":"1957-08-28","vote_average":8.087,"backdrop_path":"/BBVAUchYvkmPThVIqipgAfabfl.jpg","original_title":"Smultronstället","original_language":"sv"},{"id":424,"adult":false,"title":"Schindler's List","video":false,"overview":"The true story of how businessman Oskar Schindler saved over a thousand Jewish lives from the Nazis while they worked as slaves in his factory during World War II.","genre_ids":[18,36,10752],"popularity":14.3964,"vote_count":17144,"poster_path":"/sF1U4EUQS8YHUYjNl3pMGNIQyr0.jpg","release_date":"1993-12-15","vote_average":8.566,"backdrop_path":"/zb6fM1CX41D9rF9hdgclu0peUmy.jpg","original_title":"Schindler's List","original_language":"en"},{"id":3490,"adult":false,"title":"Drums of Fu Manchu","video":false,"overview":"The nefarious Dr. Fu Manchu searches for the keys to the tomb of Genghis Khan, in order to fulfill a prophecy that will enable him to conquer the world. His nemesi, Dr. Nayland Smith and his associates fight to keep the evil doctor from getting his hands on the keys. In 1943 the serial was edited together into a feature movie also called Drums of Fu Manchu.","genre_ids":[14,27,878,28],"popularity":0.22,"vote_count":5,"poster_path":"/sA6AB8UqfhnJ2n8GuzwXF0UBLfV.jpg","release_date":"1940-03-15","vote_average":6.1,"backdrop_path":"/1YsTBmhbeoHkHQtSWaHzdHILiJW.jpg","original_title":"Drums of Fu Manchu","original_language":"en"},{"id":1381,"adult":false,"title":"The Fountain","video":false,"overview":"Spanning over one thousand years, and three parallel stories, The Fountain is a story of love, death, spirituality, and the fragility of our existence in this world.","genre_ids":[18,12,878,10749],"popularity":3.411,"vote_count":3022,"poster_path":"/4XTf8GuCVLWolubANaKkpk62YPq.jpg","release_date":"2006-11-22","vote_average":6.905,"backdrop_path":"/9RNJ0pKYA8EQiMa0lFZ68gzeElH.jpg","original_title":"The Fountain","original_language":"en"},{"id":1712,"adult":false,"title":"Giant","video":false,"overview":"Wealthy rancher Bick Benedict and dirt-poor cowboy Jett Rink both woo Leslie Lynnton, a beautiful young woman from Maryland who is new to Texas. She marries Benedict, but she is shocked by the racial bigotry of the White Texans against the local people of Mexican descent. Rink discovers oil on a small plot of land, and while he uses his vast, new wealth to buy all the land surrounding the Benedict ranch, the Benedict's disagreement over prejudice fuels conflict that runs across generations.","genre_ids":[18,37,10749],"popularity":3.9001,"vote_count":738,"poster_path":"/wXGmfJkU83daBsqp9R8LeWguIZd.jpg","release_date":"1956-11-08","vote_average":7.604,"backdrop_path":"/sm3ErHMXQLaNdo74vbIa1JRXIXS.jpg","original_title":"Giant","original_language":"en"},{"id":272920,"adult":false,"title":"Two Harbors","video":false,"overview":"Vic's days are filled with selling sci-fi collectibles, harassing h